Jeanetta Riley, 35, a mother-of-three daughters was killed last July after she brandished a knife at two cops outside of a hospital in Sandpoint . 
  She was taken to hospital by her husband following threats she made to kill herself . 
  She pulled a knife from under a car seat and was confronted by police . 
  Officers Michael Valenzuela and Skyler Ziegler were cleared of any wrongdoing in November . 
  Jeanetta was shot and killed after she refused to put knife down . 
 